BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:TWiV 1317: Dead shrimp walking
DTSTART:20260426T040000Z
DTEND:20260426T050000Z
DTSTAMP:20260509T064410Z
UID:f8206380d0f07d29@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Podcast - TWiV
DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: This Week in Virology]\n\nTWiV explains a study show
 ing that viral DNA load in blood and saliva varied markedly with age\, tim
 e of day season\, sex\, and depended on dozens of genetic loci\, and ident
 ification of an emerging human eye disease associated with aquatic virus z
